If you need compressed SQL Server backup you can use SQLgzip. It supports all SQL Server versions starting from 2000.&lt;br /&gt;
Free fully functional version (32-bit) supports compression and TSM. (download: http://sqlgzip.com)&lt;br/ /&gt;
Additionally you can specify compression rate as standard gzip or zip protocol are used.

